# IncidentIQ — Cursor Rules

- Project: IncidentIQ RAG Application
- Working directory: C:\dev\amdocs-ai-course\projects\incidentiq\
- Always use pathlib.Path for ALL file paths (Windows compatible)
- Never hardcode secrets — use .env via pydantic-settings only
- Type hints required on every function and method signature
- Docstrings required on every class and public method
- No print() anywhere in production code — use logger exclusively
- No bare except: — always catch specific exceptions
- No magic numbers — use constants from config.py
- Async for all I/O-bound operations (LLM calls, file reads)
- FAISS index path: knowledge_base/faiss_index/
- Embedding model: all-MiniLM-L6-v2
- LLM: OpenAI gpt-4o-mini primary; Gemini gemini-2.0-flash fallback
- Document ingestion: TXT, PDF, DOCX, XLSX from data/documents/
- Stack: FastAPI + FAISS + sentence-transformers + OpenAI + Gemini + Docker